title: Townshend and Gilmour - The Tube 1985
description:

Pete Townshend and the Deep End - The Tube 1985


The Tube October 1985
Video: Pal 720 x 576 (4:3) Bitrate around 4.5Mbps 
Audio: Dolby 2.0  256Kbps

Menus and Chapters 

Recorded from air (Channel Four) onto Panasonic VHS HIFI STEREO. (Mono recording)

Transferred to PC using Power Producer.

Menus and chapters using Nero




Pete is interviewed by Jools Holland and then performs three songs,

1. Give Blood
2. Second Hand Love
3. Face The Face


The Band features.......Simon Phillips
                        Chucho Merchan
